text: Avaru (musara janangadavaru) helidaru; nivu nam'ma balige baruva munnavu nivu nam'ma balige banda balikavu nam'mannu satayisalayitu. Avaru (musa) helidaru; bahubegane, nim'modeyanu nim'ma satruvannu nasapadisi bhumiyalli nim'mannu uttaradhikarigalagi maduvanu mattu nivu enella maduviri embudannu noduvanu
